    .medium-4.cell
      %h3 
        Objectives
    .medium-6.cell.text-left
      %p 
        DataCat is designed with both data creators and data consumers in mind. By linking creators of data sets to potential users, we help to facilitate data discovery and reuse as well as data set improvement through community vetting. DataCat helps to provide:
      %ul
        %li
          Support for graduate students, postdoctoral trainees, early stage investigators, and anyone else working with data
        %li
          Example data for pilot studies
        %li
          Scientific transparency, reproducibility, and data set record preservation
      %p 
        DataCat can foster collaboration by connecting researchers with similar interests to each other and by helping users identify subject experts. Note that we seek only to provide an avenue for communication between parties. Researchers continue to have control over access to their data, and it is up to them whether they share it.
    .medium-1.cell
